description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'A Ten Minute Guided Meditation to Clear Your Mind' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This an original 10 minute guided meditation spoken and recorded by one of our own team members,  is an effective way to eliminate overthinking by clearing your mind, allowing yourself to relax and get settled into the moment.  Letting go of all sensations, feelings, impulses and distracting thoughts, we can release from our everyday stressful state of unease.  By placing your attention on your breath, you can observe the many distractions occurring in the background of your mind, allowing them to unwind, enabling us to become even more present in the moment.

Spoken Voice: Original Commentary recorded by us.
Background Music: Composed by a member of this channel.
Background Image: is an original derivative unique to this channel, Transformed from  licensed images through pixabay.com...
